trans-unit.source: Serves as the abstract base class for HTML server controls that map to HTML elements that are required to have an opening and a closing tag.
trans-unit.target: Fungerer som abstrakt basisklasse for HTML serverkontroller tilordnet HTML-elementer må ha en åpning og avslutningskode.

trans-unit.source: The most common controls with a closing tag are the `<form>`, `<table>`, `<tr>`, `<td>`, `<a>`, and `<span>` elements.
trans-unit.target: Vanligste kontrollene med avslutningskode er den `<form>`, `<table>`, `<tr>`, `<td>`, `<a>`, og `<span>` elementer.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerText%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerHtml%2A> properties allow you to manipulate the content between the opening and closing tags of HtmlContainerControl-derived controls.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerText%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerHtml%2A>egenskapene kan du endre innhold mellom innledende og avsluttende koder HtmlContainerControl avledet kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerHtml%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerText%2A>

trans-unit.source: For a list of initial property values for an instance of HtmlContainerControl, see the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: En liste med opprinnelige verdier for en forekomst av HtmlContainerControl, kan du se den <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A new instance of this class is not created directly.
trans-unit.target: En ny forekomst av denne klassen er ikke opprettet direkte.

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > If you use the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerHtml%2A> property to specify the text between the opening and closing tags of an HTML server control, the text is not HTML encoded.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION] > Hvis du bruker den <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerHtml%2A>til å angi teksten mellom innledende og avsluttende koder en HTML-serverkontroll, teksten er HTML-kodede.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerHtml%2A>

trans-unit.source: This makes it possible to embed script within HTML tags in the text.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør det mulig å bygge inn skriptet i HTML-koder i teksten.

trans-unit.source: When using the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerHtml%2A> property, be sure to validate the value to reduce security vulnerabilities.
trans-unit.target: Når du bruker den <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerHtml%2A>-egenskapen, må du validere verdien for å redusere sikkerhetsproblemer.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerHtml%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, consider using the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerText%2A> property instead.
trans-unit.target: Ellers bør du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerText%2A>egenskapen i stedet.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerText%2A>

trans-unit.source: Restores the <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl"></xref> control's view state from a previous page request that was saved by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.SaveViewState*> method.
trans-unit.target: Gjenoppretter den <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl"> </xref> kontrollens visningen tilstand fra forrige side forespørselen som ble lagret i den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.SaveViewState*>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.SaveViewState*>

trans-unit.source: This method is used primarily by the .NET Framework infrastructure and is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden brukes hovedsakelig av .NET Framework-infrastruktur og skal ikke brukes direkte fra koden.

trans-unit.source: However, control developers can override this method to specify how a custom server control restores its view state.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollutviklere kan imidlertid overstyre denne metoden hvis du vil angi hvordan en egendefinert serverkontroll gjenoppretter visningstilstanden.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [ASP.NET State Management Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [ASP.NET oversikt over tilstand](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The LoadViewState method calls the base class's <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.LoadViewState%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Metoden LoadViewState kaller basisklassen <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.LoadViewState%2A>metode.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.LoadViewState%2A>

trans-unit.source: In addition, the LoadViewState method sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerHtml%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg metoden LoadViewState angir den <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerHtml%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlContainerControl.InnerHtml%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that represents the control state to be restored.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object>som representerer tilstanden kontrollen skal gjenopprettes.</xref:System.Object>
